{"tid":795232,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"徐加晴患怪病入院 香港無藥可醫","createTime":"2018-08-27T00:00:13.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-27T00:42:49.000Z","uid":13468,"like":6,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"531798881f5a0f2608bed3b263f3450f9a92cc1b","tid":795232,"uid":13468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T00:00:13.000Z","msg":"跟「蝦頭」楊詩敏撞樣的樂壇新人徐加晴（Rona）前日又屙又嘔，頭暈兼頭痛要緊急入院留醫，昨日仍留院的她受訪時表示：「個病叫『cryptosporidium』（小隱孢子蟲），最大問題係香港冇醫呢種病嘅藥，要搵外國專家睇吓邊隻藥啱我，藥費要成萬蚊，未有藥食前，我要繼續留院打止屙針、吊鹽水同葡萄水先。」最心痛是她因停工，錯失數萬元商演機會。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.celebrity.yahoo.com/%E5%BE%90%E5%8A%A0%E6%99%B4%E6%82%A3%E6%80%AA%E7%97%85%E5%85%A5%E9%99%A2-%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E7%84%A1%E8%97%A5%E5%8F%AF%E9%86%AB-214500585.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.celebrity.yahoo.com%2F%25E5%25BE%2590%25E5%258A%25A0%25E6%2599%25B4%25E6%2582%25A3%25E6%2580%25AA%25E7%2597%2585%25E5%2585%25A5%25E9%2599%25A2-%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E7%2584%25A1%25E8%2597%25A5%25E5%258F%25AF%25E9%2586%25AB-214500585.html&d=ZGIDNEE%2FQoc1KCe8%2F31F0DOU%2Fspzl0GStOx2So8CiJ8%3D&h=900be724\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.celebrity.yahoo.com/%E5%BE%90%E5%8A%A0%E6%99%B4%E6%82%A3%E6%80%AA%E7%97%85%E5%85%A5%E9%99%A2-%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E7%84%A1%E8%97%A5%E5%8F%AF%E9%86%AB-214500585.html</a>"},{"pid":"53f9c923fcc5948da2a9fa4161fdc5a1a47a3658","tid":795232,"uid":85557,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T00:14:13.000Z","msg":"Who"},{"pid":"de7931582a3331b30fe6599dc73cd4243eb82609","tid":795232,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T00:42:49.000Z","msg":"時事？"}]}